name: "DuAugH!"
description: This is a video created by my brother @evanriley308 featuring my father waxing his nose hair. The video was uploaded to TikTok on 6/4/2020 and has  accrued over 728k views at the time of this tweet.  I am minting this video on my brother's behalf in order  to raise funds to repair damage caused by his recent  sequence of bad luck. He threw a metal BB at his friend's car on a hot Florida afternoon and comepletely shattered his windshield. He was also involved in a minor fender-bender a few days later. Cars are complicated.
